parameters.name: InitialUser
parameters.description: The user who executes the query statement.

parameters.name: Keyword
parameters.description: The keyword of the query statement.

parameters.name: PageSize
parameters.description: The number of entries per page.

parameters.name: QueryDurationMs
parameters.description: The execution duration of slow SQL queries. Minimum value: 1000. Unit: milliseconds.

parameters.name: QueryOrder
parameters.description:
Specifies the columns by which the query results are sorted in descending order.

*   0: The query results are sorted by the query_duration_ms column.
*   1: The query results are sorted by the query_duration_ms and query_start_time columns.
*   2: The query results are sorted by the query_duration_ms, query_start_time, and user columns.
